imdb.plot outline: Jake Steinfeld, Hollywood's Trainer to the Stars, leads three solid workouts on one dynamic release aimed at steering you down the path of total body fitness. Make Jake's way yours - and feel better and stronger soon! Combines three great programs: Total Body Workout, Lower Body Workout, and Awesome Abba Dabbas Abdominal Workout.
